{"tid":2375352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警要拉大型橙帶喇 !!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2021-01-22T03:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T08:21:56.000Z","uid":70964,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"faca4398fce62f3361f220f0edc6784785c0a0bd","tid":2375352,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xAPmL5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxAPmL5Q.jpg&h=3204415d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個疫區要鎖"},{"pid":"7d0f401aebee8258ac99c679955f4913e89251f6","tid":2375352,"uid":44732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:30:33.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"7b0e982fb4e5d2d4d463d1110906aa64a7ba721c","tid":2375352,"uid":8294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"高登 / 黃金 / 鴨記<br />\n收皮"},{"pid":"6b0520a9f1450d47214bd52ef7a8963fa35bad9d","tid":2375352,"uid":373438,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:37:15.000Z","msg":"今鋪雞蟲又要留喺屋企打飛機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd61a265f330f0858e643b89c5b1617ebc3096e","tid":2375352,"uid":70964,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7d0f401aebee8258ac99c679955f4913e89251f6","tid":2375352,"uid":44732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:30:33.000Z","msg":"source?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"購物用膳限區內 店舖禁區外補貨<br />\n<br />\n向居民提供物資 目標3天驗全區 <br />\n<br />\n有知情人士表示，方案下，圍封期間在強檢區內或已進區內的人，須持有陰性檢測報告才可離開，但區內人仍可在區內活動，例如購買日用品及到餐廳用膳，但店舖的貨品賣完便不准從外補貨。政府內部估計區內有逾1萬人，有望圍封兩三天便可完成區內全民檢測，之後解封，其間政府會在區內為有需要者提供基本物資等支援。他強調，據他了解政府未有定案，若準備過程順利，在周末進行是最佳時間，因較多人不用上班，若在兩三天完成，區內市民在上班日可如常上班，但仍要視乎檢測進度。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，昨午有不同紀律部隊前線人員陸續收到指示，要求今日起至周日取消休假，協助保安局執行「特別防疫任務」。有紀律部隊將有關人手分成兩更，每更14小時，有關工時可當「超時補水」處理，最快今晚9時聽取詳細工作安排，故有前線人員估計最快明日（周六）凌晨執行有關安排。<br />\n<br />\n有前線不滿當局「強制交人」<br />\n<br />\n憂惹反彈「要對居民動武」 <br />\n<br />\n該前線人員表示以往抗疫工作為自願參與，不滿今次「強制交人」，憂「禁足」會引起區內市民反彈，屆時或要對普通市民使用武力，但他沒受過正統群眾管理訓練，亦無接受醫療訓練，「呢啲留番警察做」，亦擔心是次開壞先例，日後「用國安、反恐、抗疫等名義，來做政治任務」。"},{"pid":"9ccb2c9029175436d593dddc1f1331b28cf6947b","tid":2375352,"uid":70964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b0e982fb4e5d2d4d463d1110906aa64a7ba721c","tid":2375352,"uid":8294,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"高登 / 黃金 / 鴨記<br />\n收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:40:06.000Z","msg":"呢幾日已經死死地.."},{"pid":"cda83430be47ff673635c9e801d728b52ae22d62","tid":2375352,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"放tear gas <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4e4d3790eeba6f6974cc7f0fe0548244b31f02","tid":2375352,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced8aace3c3d9be3bf8d4351afb7192fe2d758da","tid":2375352,"uid":70964,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cda83430be47ff673635c9e801d728b52ae22d62","tid":2375352,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:40:36.000Z","msg":"放tear gas <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r55pJXk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://